<div>
  <span>Name</span>
  <%= form.text_field :name %>
</div>
	
<div>
  <span>1. What type of web developer are you?</span>
  <%= form.radio_button :web_dev_type, 1 %>Full-Stack
  <%= form.radio_button :web_dev_type, 2 %>Front-End
  <%= form.radio_button :web_dev_type, 3 %>Back-End
</div>

<div>
  <span>2. What’s your current employment status?</span>
  <%= form.radio_button :employment_status, true %>Employed
  <%= form.radio_button :employment_status, false %>Not Employed
</div>

<div>
	<p>(If not employed, skip to question #5)<p>
</div>

<div>
  <span>3. What best describes your position?</span>
  <%= form.radio_button :position_type, 1 %>Full-time
  <%= form.radio_button :position_type, 2 %>Temp-to-Perm
  <%= form.radio_button :position_type, 3 %>Freelance
</div>

<div>
  <span>4. Did you find the position through our Outcomes Program?</span>
  <%= form.radio_button :found_thru_outcomes, true %>Yes
  <%= form.radio_button :found_thru_outcomes, false %>No
</div>

<div>
  <span>5. Please share your Company Name</span>
  <%= form.text_field :company %>
  <span>and your Start Date</span>
  <%= form.date_field :employment_date %>
</div>

<div>
  <span>6. The technical skills I learned during my immersive course has properly prepared me for real-life work environments.</span>
  <%= form.radio_buttons :enough_preparation, 1 %>I disagree
  <%= form.radio_buttons :enough_preparation, 2 %>I somewhat disagree
  <%= form.radio_buttons :enough_preparation, 3 %>Neutral feelings
  <%= form.radio_buttons :enough_preparation, 4 %>I somewhat agree
  <%= form.radio_buttons :enough_preparation, 5 %>I completely agree
</div>

<div>
  <span>7. How would you rate the effectiveness of your Officer’s involvement in your job search preparation and actual job search?</span>
  <%= form.radio_buttons :officer_effectiveness, 1 %>Ineffective
  <%= form.radio_buttons :officer_effectiveness, 2 %>Somewhat effective
  <%= form.radio_buttons :officer_effectiveness, 3 %>Stellar!
</div>

<div>
	<p>Tell us in your own words:<p>
</div>   

<div>
  <span>8. What hard/soft skills that you didn’t learn while at GA would have better prepared you post-graduation, whether or not you’ve already found a job.</span>
  <%= form.text_field :should_have_learned %>
</div>    

<div>
  <span>9. If you’re currently not employed, what are some hurdles you’ve encountered during your job search?</span>
  <%= form.text_field :hurdles %>
</div> 

<div>
  <span>10. Anything else you want to say?</span>
  <%= form.text_field :anything_else %>
</div> 





			